How Spring Security hooks to Central Authentication Service (CAS)=> http://mattfleming.com/node/269


Username-password pair corresponds to the key-value pair under <property name="users">. For 4.0.0, it's username = casuser, password = Mellon.

take a look at the deployerConfigContext.xml file.



